This website is created for educational purposes only. Its main goal is to help students learn about website creation, coding, and basic web development concepts.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time as the website develops. Any changes will be posted on this page.

Thank you for visiting our learning website and supporting student education.
